Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and the effects of image degradations on it. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses deep-learning neural networks for image classification. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper deals with training and improving the performance of CNN-based image classification. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with different types of degraded images and their effects on image classification. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and the effects of image degradations on image classification.
